  m_text: "EMPLOYEE HANDBOOK  \n\nSec 1: Your Workspace\nWelcome to the night shift.
    Your shift will end when your daily quota is met. Not a minute sooner.\n\nThe
    SLA (Service Level Agreement):\nTime is money. You are constantly being timed.
    If you take too long to answer a ringing phone, or if you sit on an open line
    without progressing the conversation, you will receive a STRIKE.\n\nAccumulate
    enough STRIKES, and your employment will be permanently terminated.\n\n"
