  m_text: 'Sec 2: Client Relations

    You are the voice of our corporation. Professionalism
    is mandatory.


    - Most clients simply want to be heard. Use the TALK button
    to progress through their dialogue. Once their issue is resolved, the system
    will automatically disconnect the call. You do not need to manually hang up.


    -
    Some of our high-value clients value their time more than your life. They will
    hang up and issue a complaint (Strike) if you let the phone ring for more than
    a few seconds. Watch your Caller ID and answer swiftly.'
